#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Solve the cube.</action> This shows all your moves being undone, "
"then all the shuffling moves being undone and then the shuffling moves being "
"re-done, leaving you set up to have another go at the puzzle."
msgstr ""
"<action>Resolve o cubo.</action> Isto mostra todas as suas jogadas a serem "
"anuladas e depois todas as jogadas para baralhar a serem anuladas e, "
"finalmente, o acto de baralhar a ser repetido, deixando-o pronto para tentar "
"de novo o 'puzzle'."

#. Tag: menuchoice
