"&kubrick; was inspired by Professor Ern&odblac; Rubik's famous "
"<trademark>Rubik's Cube </trademark> puzzle."
msgstr ""
"O &kubrick; foi inspirado pelo famoso 'puzzle' <trademark>Cubo de Rubik</"
"trademark> (ou <trademark>Cubo Mágico</trademark>) do Professor Ern&odblac; "
"Rubik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
